PhoneInbasketWorkunitFolderContextForm is a Form
    title is "RelatedLink"
    Layout
        single column
            Name
            DocType
            Value
                use text area of 5 lines
        single column
            button of "Open"
                visible when (PfiWorkunit.NoActionRequest)
                link is "<Url>&context.session.key.ui_type=SMARTPHONE&context.session.key.noheader=true"
        single column
            AttachBy
                display as text
            AttachDate
                display as text
            text of "<AttachByName>"
